{
  "slug": "the-five-most-anticipated-movies-of-the-fall-festivals-plus-",
  "title": "The Five Most Anticipated Movies of the Fall Festivals. Plus: 'The Irishman' Is Almost Here ... and It's Three and a Half Hours Long",
  "show": "The Big Picture",
  "network": "The Ringer",
  "hosts": [
