          "title": "Dark Waters",
          "year": 2019,
          "note": "Todd Haynes's toxic-tort docudrama with Mark Ruffalo and Anne Hathaway, scripted by Anthony McCarten. She's fascinated by how far it sits from Haynes's usual register."
        },
        {
          "title": "Knives Out",
          "year": 2019,
          "note": "Rian Johnson's whodunit with Daniel Craig and Chris Evans, premiering at TIFF. She calls it exactly her kind of movie and doubts the Oscars will agree."
